@page "/help"
@rendermode InteractiveServer

<PageTitle>Help</PageTitle>

<h1>Help</h1>

<h3>How to Use the App</h3>

<p>
    The Recipe Meal Planner app helps users organize recipes, plan meals,
    and manage grocery lists.
</p>

<h4>Recipes</h4>
<p>
    Go to the Recipes page to view saved recipes. From there, users can add,
    edit, or delete recipes.
</p>

<h4>Meal Planner</h4>
<p>
    Go to the Meal Planner page to choose a recipe, select a meal type, and
    assign it to a specific date.
</p>

<h4>Grocery List</h4>
<p>
    Go to the Grocery List page to add grocery items, mark items as purchased,
    or delete items from the list.
</p>

<h4>Navigation</h4>
<p>
    Use the navigation menu to move between Home, Recipes, Meal Planner,
    Grocery List, and Help.
</p>